<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Toyota Excellence | 2026 Innovation</title>
    <style>
        /* CSS Styling */
        :root {
            --toyota-red: #eb0a1e;
            --dark-grey: #333;
            --light-grey: #f4f4f4;
        }

        body {
            font-family: 'Segoe UI', Tahoma, Geneva, Verdana, sans-serif;
            margin: 0;
            line-height: 1.6;
            color: #333;
        }

        header {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 1rem 5%;
            display: flex;
            justify-content: space-between;
            align-items: center;
            box-shadow: 0 2px 5px rgba(0,0,0,0.1);
            position: sticky;
            top: 0;
            z-index: 1000;
        }

        .logo {
            font-size: 1.5rem;
            font-weight: bold;
            color: var(--toyota-red);
            text-decoration: none;
        }

        nav a {
            margin-left: 20px;
            text-decoration: none;
            color: var(--dark-grey);
            font-weight: 500;
        }

        .hero {
            background: linear-gradient(rgba(0,0,0,0.6), rgba(0,0,0,0.6)), 
                        url('https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1621259182978-f09e5e2aa88a?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=2000');
            background-size: cover;
            background-position: center;
            height: 60vh;
            display: flex;
            flex-direction: column;
            justify-content: center;
            align-items: center;
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 0 20px;
        }

        .hero h1 { font-size: 3rem; margin-bottom: 10px; }

        .container { padding: 40px 5%; }

        .grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 20px;
            margin-top: 20px;
        }

        .card {
            background: var(--light-grey);
            padding: 20px;
            border-radius: 8px;
            transition: transform 0.3s;
        }

        .card:hover { transform: translateY(-5px); }

        .card img {
            width: 100%;
            height: 200px;
            object-fit: cover;
            border-radius: 5px;
        }

        .specs {
            background: #fff;
            padding: 10px;
            border-left: 4px solid var(--toyota-red);
            margin-top: 10px;
            font-size: 0.9rem;
        }

        footer {
            background: var(--dark-grey);
            color: white;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 20px;
            margin-top: 40px;
        }
    </style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <a href="#" class="logo">TOYOTA</a>
    <nav>
        <a href="#lineup">2026 Lineup</a>
        <a href="#history">Our History</a>
        <a href="#safety">Safety</a>
    </nav>
</header>

<section class="hero">
    <h1>Lead the Way</h1>
    <p>Discover the 2026 Toyota Collection: Reliability meets Future Tech.</p>
</section>

<div class="container" id="lineup">
    <h2>Featured 2026 Models</h2>
    <div class="grid">
        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1623860841270-2a628399994b?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Toyota Corolla">
            <h3>Corolla Hybrid</h3>
            <p>The world's most popular sedan, now with 5th Gen Hybrid technology.</p>
            <div class="specs">
                <strong>Est. MPG:</strong> 53 City / 46 Hwy<br>
                <strong>Key Feature:</strong> 12.3-inch Digital Cockpit
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1594502184342-2e12f877aa73?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Toyota RAV4">
            <h3>RAV4 Plug-In</h3>
            <p>Unmatched versatility with class-leading electric range.</p>
            <div class="specs">
                <strong>Power:</strong> 306 HP<br>
                <strong>EV Range:</strong> Up to 75 km
            </div>
        </div>

        <div class="card">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1616455579100-2ceaa4eb2d37?auto=format&fit=crop&q=80&w=800" alt="Toyota Tacoma">
            <h3>Tacoma i-FORCE MAX</h3>
            <p>The ultimate adventure machine with a redesigned hybrid powertrain.</p>
            <div class="specs">
                <strong>Drive:</strong> 4WD with TRD Off-Road options<br>
                <strong>Tech:</strong> Toyota Safety Sense 3.0
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</div>

<div class="container" id="history" style="background: #f9f9f9;">
    <h2>The Toyota Legacy</h2>
    <p>Founded in <strong>1937</strong> by Kiichiro Toyoda, Toyota has grown from a textile loom manufacturer into the world's largest automaker. Known for the <em>Toyota Production System</em>, the brand is synonymous with Quality, Durability, and Reliability (QDR).</p>
    <ul>
        <li><strong>1966:</strong> The first Corolla is launched.</li>
        <li><strong>1997:</strong> The Prius debuts as the first mass-produced hybrid.</li>
        <li><strong>2026:</strong> Expanding the "Beyond Zero" (bZ) electric lineup.</li>
    </ul>
</div>

<footer>
    <p>&copy; 2026 Toyota Fan Site | Created for Educational Purposes</p>
</footer>

</body>
</html>